my, Ramasamy}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1949 births]]\n[[Category:People from Perak]]\n[[Category:Malaysian people of Tamil descent]]\n[[Category:Malaysian people of Indian descent]]\n[[Category:Malaysian politicians of Indian descent]]\n[[Category:Democratic Action Party (Malaysia) politicians]]\n[[Category:Members of the Dewan Rakyat]]\n[[Category:Members of the Penang State Legislative Assembly]]\n[[Category:Penang state executive councillors]]\n[[Category:Academics of the National University of Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Indiana University alumni]]\n[[Category:McGill University alumni]]\n[[Category:University of Malaya alumni]]\n[[Category:21st-century Malaysian politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century Malaysian people]]\n", "name_user": "Bearcat", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:duplicate categorization; already in subcat", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramasamy_Palanisamy"}
